<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Genomics on Kaya Log</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/</link><description>Recent content in Genomics on Kaya Log</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Download Influenza virus genome sequence from GISAID database</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/genomics-gisiad/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/genomics-gisiad/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="download-influenza-virus-genome-sequence-from-gisaid-database">
 Download Influenza virus genome sequence from GISAID database
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#download-influenza-virus-genome-sequence-from-gisaid-database">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="0829">
 0829
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#0829">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>GISAID 계정생성.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://gisaid.org/">GISAID&lt;/a>에 들어가서 login을 클릭하면 sign up 창이 있다. 넘어가서 Register를 눌러준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/59f14604-5b30-43d8-8e47-00d897cc6fb2" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>GISAID 사용자 계정을 받기위한 개인사업자등록 양식을 작성해줘야한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/02049d8c-18a3-4784-b5c2-e16e36243678" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>입력한 이메일로 온 링크로 들어가면 이 화면이 뜬다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/93aef75d-8bb1-4bc9-9d59-338483276013" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>아직 로그인은 안되는듯.. 왜냐면 비밀번호를 친적이없음 ㅠㅠ&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="0830">
 0830
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#0830">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>계정생성 승인이 넘느린거같아서 그냥 연구실 계정을 받았다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2eab579e-e840-4b86-afc8-d752396baf4d" alt="image" />&lt;/p>
&lt;p>로그인을 하면 이렇게뜬다. 근데 내가 받고싶은 EpiFlu 빼고 다 클릭됨&amp;hellip;&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Biomart; convert ensembl id into gene symbol</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/genomics-biomart/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/bioinformatics/genomics/genomics-biomart/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="biomart-convert-ensembl-id-into-gene-symbol">
 Biomart; convert ensembl id into gene symbol
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#biomart-convert-ensembl-id-into-gene-symbol">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="1-사전-설치">
 1. 사전 설치
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-%ec%82%ac%ec%a0%84-%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>아래 코드로 Biomart를 설치해준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-R" data-lang="R">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> (&lt;span style="color:#f92672">!&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">requireNamespace&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;BiocManager&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, quietly &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">TRUE&lt;/span>))
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">install.packages&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;BiocManager&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>BiocManager&lt;span style="color:#f92672">::&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">install&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;biomaRt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>설치가 완료되었다면 R 환경과 Biomart 패키지의 버전을 확인해보자.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-R" data-lang="R">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>R.version
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-plain" data-lang="plain">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> _
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>platform x86_64-conda-linux-gnu
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>arch x86_64
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>os linux-gnu
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>system x86_64, linux-gnu
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>major 4
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>minor 0.5
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>year 2021
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>month 03
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>day 31
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>svn rev 80133
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>language R
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>version.string R version 4.0.5 (2021-03-31)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>nickname Shake and Throw
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-R" data-lang="R">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">packageVersion&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;biomaRt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-plain" data-lang="plain">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>[1] &amp;#39;2.46.3&amp;#39;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>나의 경우 R(4.0.5), Biomart(2.46.3)을 사용해주었다. 참고로 R(&amp;gt;=2.1) 버전을 필요로 한다.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>